{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>《Lullabye》是一款設計精美的環境音混合器，專為那些夜間難以入睡、渴望寧靜安眠的使用者打造。它能協助您快速進入夢鄉，擺脫日常噪音的干擾，今天這款實用 App </p>\n    <p><ref href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/category/apps-情報/限時免費情報/\" target=\"_blank\">限時免費</ref>中，正是您改善睡眠品質的最佳時機，千萬不要錯過。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-95.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>打造個人化的專屬助眠氛圍</h2>\n    <p>《Lullabye》讓您能自由疊加雨聲、海浪聲等多種環境音效，並個別調整音量，打造專屬助眠情境。它內建睡眠計時器，聲音會溫和漸弱，引導您輕鬆入睡。此應用還支援背景運作，全程無廣告，為您提供純粹、寧靜的睡眠體驗。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-76-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-77-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-78-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1290x2796bb-79-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-26T16:24:52.674183+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":230,"images":5,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}